            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="1c06-5502-fb5a-616e">Set a Shade token Wholly Within 12&quot; of any model in this Unit. At the End of the Round, the controlling player may set all models of this Unit in Coherency, treating the Shade token as the Leading Model. The Shade token has DISPLACEMENT.</characteristic>
