          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="1c06-5502-fb5a-616e">Set a Force Field token Within 8&quot; in an unoccupied space. Units of Size 2 or lower cannot move across Force Fields. Models of Size 3 or more can move over it, and it&apos;s then removed.</characteristic>
